{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "A [GERMAN] is a-- a [GERMAN] is a room where-- where-- it was the whole brain of the factory-- of the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Buttons and switches.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was instructing me, because the guy that was-- that was supposed to be there was-- took sick or something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I should work there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "For about a couple hours, he was showing me all the lights, and the switches, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he was watching me whether I do the-- the proper things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I-- I was doing it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But really, my mind was elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I couldn't concentrate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Those days, I could not concentrate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I was-- my mind was always in my family back home and with my situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And after a few hours, finally I-- I heard a-- a big crash.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And I didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Apparently I pushed-- pulled the wrong switch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- the elevators that were taking down the-- the workers were knocked out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "This Obersteiger, this so-called friend of mine, he came down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "He's beating the-- the daylight out of me, what I caused.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The whole-- the whole coal mine was-- was-- was stranded in that coal mine for a few hours-- it'd be for 10 hours.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But once they-- they-- they fixed it, the SA came down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They grabbed me-- not only me, all my friends, whoever was friendly with me-- and they arrested us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they brought us to the Polizeipraesidium, which is the-- which is the Gestapo, the name of the Gestapo, in the main city of Bochum.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they brought us to Bochum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I cannot-- it's hard to describe how tortured I was in that cell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I mean, in that-- in that prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Investigations.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
